complaining about the noise.

105
00:08:28,170 --> 00:08:30,445
It's late. Do it later.

106
00:08:45,610 --> 00:08:47,083
Can we move?

107
00:08:53,506 --> 00:08:54,581
Why all of a sudden?

108
00:08:56,348 --> 00:09:01,086
I want to live where I can
open the windows all the way.

109
00:09:05,963 --> 00:09:07,365
