127
00:10:28,631 --> 00:10:29,920
Just humor them.

128
00:10:31,151 --> 00:10:33,784
Fine. But please smoke outside.

129
00:10:54,998 --> 00:10:56,052
Hello?

130
00:10:56,473 --> 00:10:58,328
Are you Korea Daily's Han Ji-won?

131
00:10:59,214 --> 00:11:00,586
Yes, this is she.

132
00:11:00,669 --> 00:11:02,682
I'm calling from Bokuk Daily's HR team.

133
00:11:02,765 --> 00:11:06,062
I can go near Korea Daily's office
in about two hours.

134
00:11:06,145 --> 00:11:07,425
Shall we meet for a moment?

135
00:11:07,508 --> 00:11:10,088
I can, but what is this about?

136
00:11:10,815 --> 00:11:12,274
To offer you a position.

137
00:11:13,542 --> 00:11:14,546
Pardon?

138
00:11:19,901 --> 00:11:21,832
