146
00:11:49,157 --> 00:11:51,630
It'll really ruin her at this rate.

147
00:11:52,132 --> 00:11:53,386
Yes. Right now?

148
00:11:53,469 --> 00:11:56,397
I came to feed Hyun-joo's dog,
and now I'm on my way to the lawyer.

149
00:12:17,499 --> 00:12:18,944
What's your job?

150
00:12:19,845 --> 00:12:20,838
