151
00:12:22,196 --> 00:12:25,034
I messaged you to ask you
to come down after ten minutes.

152
00:12:25,117 --> 00:12:26,052
You messaged me?

153
00:12:29,405 --> 00:12:30,856
Did you say you messaged me?

154
00:12:32,363 --> 00:12:34,050
I left home early,

155
00:12:34,133 --> 00:12:36,860
but there was an accident
on Inner Ring Expressway.

156
00:12:36,943 --> 00:12:40,389
The exits are few and far between there.
I'm so sorry.

157
00:12:40,472 --> 00:12:42,007
It's basic to be on time.

158
00:12:42,090 --> 00:12:43,570
Also, look at the car.

159
00:12:45,154 --> 00:12:47,015
I got a car wash yesterday,

160
00:12:47,098 --> 00:12:50,014
but it rained overnight.

161
00:12:50,097 --> 00:12:53,023
I couldn't look after it today.

162
00:12:53,106 --> 00:12:54,212
I'm so sorry.

163
00:12:54,963 --> 00:12:57,840
You never tried preparing in advance,
have you?

164
00:12:57,923 --> 00:12:59,326
Today was an exception.

165
00:12:59,409 --> 00:13:00,455
I'll get things right next time, sir.

166
00:13:00,538 --> 00:13:02,179
Why always next time?

167
00:13:09,265 --> 00:13:12,383
Do you know what's common
among people like you?

168
00:13:14,180 --> 00:13:15,274
You're lazy,

169
00:13:16,837 --> 00:13:17,953
impatient,

170
00:13:18,887 --> 00:13:20,257
and full of excuses.

171
00:13:26,319 --> 00:13:27,363
Honey!

172
00:13:27,446 --> 00:13:30,594
Mr. Kim, wake up.

173
00:13:31,974 --> 00:13:34,091
