176
00:13:40,177 --> 00:13:41,340
Step aside.

177
00:13:44,747 --> 00:13:45,725
Keep your mouth shut.

178
00:13:53,040 --> 00:13:54,841
Gosh, it's hot.

179
00:14:01,151 --> 00:14:02,333
Do you feel wronged?

180
00:14:04,281 --> 00:14:07,096
After all, you did send a text.

181
00:14:07,179 --> 00:14:08,577
What could be the problem?

182
00:14:16,382 --> 00:14:17,330
Hey.

183
00:14:20,911 --> 00:14:22,473
I'm sorry, Sir.

184
00:14:22,556 --> 00:14:24,816
This won't ever happen again.

185
00:14:24,899 --> 00:14:26,367
It was nice having you.

186
00:14:31,940 --> 00:14:32,965
Sir.

187
00:14:33,857 --> 00:14:36,218
Sir, I'll fix my mistake.

188
00:14:36,793 --> 00:14:37,691
Sir.

189
00:14:38,775 --> 00:14:39,910
Sir.

190
00:14:52,084 --> 00:14:53,093
Ta-da.

191
00:14:54,144 --> 00:14:56,189
What is this?

192
00:14:58,992 --> 00:15:02,501
You mentioned you used to like
the Crazy Donut in front of our school.

193
00:15:05,056 --> 00:15:06,070
Oh.

194
00:15:07,268 --> 00:15:08,607
I was reminded of you,

195
00:15:08,690 --> 00:15:11,038
so I went there in a hurry
just before going to the airport.

196
00:15:11,121 --> 00:15:12,372
Are you proud of me?

197
00:15:14,011 --> 00:15:15,896
Yes. Thank you.

198
00:15:15,979 --> 00:15:17,613
It didn't even cross my mind.

199
00:15:17,696 --> 00:15:21,909
Ms. Lee, I heard you're a professor now.

200
00:15:21,992 --> 00:15:23,417
Congratulations.

201
00:17:26,152 --> 00:17:27,176
