and we can get evaluated on it.

319
00:27:09,913 --> 00:27:10,876
Okay?

320
00:27:17,307 --> 00:27:18,606
Didn't I tell you?

321
00:27:19,602 --> 00:27:22,339
My assistant will join me
to and from work starting today.

322
00:27:23,380 --> 00:27:25,445
-Mr. Jung?
-No, my secretary.

323
00:27:27,500 --> 00:27:28,517
You're here.

